 100:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****           To correctly read data from FLASH memory, the number of wait states (LATENCY) 
 101:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****           must be correctly programmed according to the frequency of the CPU clock 
 102:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****           (HCLK) and the supply voltage of the device.
 103:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****     [..]      
 104:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****       For STM32F405xx/07xx and STM32F415xx/17xx devices
