 730:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   * @note   This function must be used when the device voltage range is from
 731:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   *         2.7V to 3.6V and an External Vpp is present.
