 733:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   * @note   If an erase and a program operations are requested simultaneously,    
 734:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   *         the erase operation is performed before the program one.
 735:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   *  
 736:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   * @param  Address: specifies the address to be programmed.
 737:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   * @param  Data: specifies the data to be programmed.
 738:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   * @retval FLASH Status: The returned value can be: FLASH_BUSY, FLASH_ERROR_PROGRAM,
 739:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_flash.c ****   *                       FLASH_ERROR_WRP, FLASH_ERROR_OPERATION or FLASH_COMPLETE.
